snippet.title: Puma Street Soccer Playstation Gameplay
snippet.description:
Hey look...multi upload...basically I couldn't decide on which one to upload first between this and Live Wire so I thought why not, upload both in the one day and do so in alphabectical order. Plus it makes sense because I'm five years behind on uploads and being away Saturday with my wife doesn't help.

Anyways, here's something I haven't looked at in a while...okay I'm lying because it's soccer again, but Street Soccer is something's I've only looked at once before when I did Chris Kamara's Street Soccer waaaay back...and this is by the same developers so it'll make sense to compare the two of them.

Oh, and having said I'll go back to its intro tune in the video I never did....the intro video tune believe it or not is Freak on a Leash by Korn which I have a feeling was never licensed for use.....yikes.

Current Soccer record: 3-9
